{"tid":394969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新亞書院舊生鄧家彪認為「乃共」係欺師滅祖既行為","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T02:00:59.000Z","uid":33307,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"045108b13d7431b4cd2e83b2f06181001bfbe1c0","tid":394969,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"奶共又唔比，港獨又唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身是新亞書院舊生的前立法會議員鄧家彪，斥責學生的行為是「欺師滅祖、目無尊長」。他批評學生在書中使用了錯誤格式，內容亦講不出大道理，更坦言學生愈是有這種行為，社會就愈是痛心，形容涉事學生是「新亞之恥」，除了應該向院長道歉之外，更應該向全社會道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.read01.com/uploads/0EiN8Wq3II.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0EiN8Wq3II.jpg&h=2e190c98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5160719517b886f65b028ae1765ed7acc4d27341","tid":394969,"uid":34869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"欺師滅祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n華山派定全真教"},{"pid":"4d815caddf790bf09342d47827a25992b68c81f3","tid":394969,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欺師滅祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n華山派定全真教</blockquote><br />\n武當呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c6b4ac84707f9b9db0f44f9433644390ab7768","tid":394969,"uid":53687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"工賊會炸死無辜姊弟又係乜道理？"},{"pid":"d8a0562ded5f2c0e5924bdbea20470661a346b91","tid":394969,"uid":54959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"佢噏乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866f753739ca9a28fd0ec9b67e61601a