normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲格式係抄奶共院長撚返佢架嘛<br />\n<br />\nbtw 新亞學生高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b16c55704da7b0d972c474ad7f2a3945d23e7f","tid":394969,"uid":2857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"個上款好明顯係炒垃圾院長黃乃共啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個垃圾老師仲好興奮咁以為捉到錯處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93a7e0a274a0471d323c6dc5ee006605441d24c","tid":394969,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"撚狗成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf801ddb1fd1dc33d3260acb3647e3f50c9eba6","tid":394969,"uid":55290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個上款好明顯係炒垃圾院長黃乃共啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個垃圾老師仲好興奮咁以為捉到錯處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢條教畜真係叻唔切，比人撚都唔知，柒撚到。仲講文憑試扣分真係笑撚死人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNASU啲人公開試成績分分鐘好撚過呢條垃圾教畜啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講埋啲咁幾野水平有限，垃圾教畜為份糧害死幾撚多學生。"},{"pid":"178b231db79cd7d010a3f4fe4d5468d3d827c1f7","tid":394969,"uid":25329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"但係睇cctvb果啲廢中 廢老會認為學生唔識字係垃圾 唔會知係撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7e0942d502f9282d9e1dbb187bd8503200cf51","tid":394969